<li id="cite_note-67"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-67">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Glancy (1995), pp. 4–5. Schatz (1998) says the production cost of <i>Lights of New York</i> totaled $75,000 (p. 64). Even if this number is accurate, the rate of return was still over 1,600%.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-68"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-68">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Robertson (2001), p. 180.</span>
