<li id="cite_note-F87-105"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-F87_105-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-F87_105-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Freiberg (1987), p. 76.</span>
