<li id="cite_note-108"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-108">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Quoted in <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSharp,_Jasper2002" class="citation web cs1">Sharp, Jasper (March 7, 2002). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.midnighteye.com/features/silentfilm_pt1.shtml">"<i>A Page of Madness</i> (1927)"</a>. Midnight Eye<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">December 7,</span> 2009</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=A+Page+of+Madness+%281927%29&amp;rft.pub=Midnight+Eye&amp;rft.date=2002-03-07&amp;rft.au=Sharp%2C+Jasper&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.midnighteye.com%2Ffeatures%2Fsilentfilm_pt1.shtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASound+film" class="Z3988"></span></span>
